==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Seen
<hw>Seen</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Versed; skilled; accomplished.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Well <qex>seen</qex> in every science that mote be.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Noble Boyle, not less in nature <qex>seen</qex>,⟦br⟧
